title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
subtitle: GTA+
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (September 5 - October 2) will also receive:

— The Enus Deity (Sedan)
— Special Weekly Rewards
— Access to The Vinewood Club Workshop
— 2X GTA$ and RP on Madrazo Daily Bounties and Contact Missions
— The Green 247 Shirt and Khaki 247 Chino Pants
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
